{"tid":2289696,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"孟晚舟引渡案   關鍵證人 Ben Chang 拒絕出庭作證","createTime":"2020-11-17T12:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T13:20:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a13c9943ed2eeab4b057bd0ad3fc306b682bbbc2","tid":2289696,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1605582964933&amp;issue=20201117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1605582964933%26issue%3D20201117&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4%2FBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=992c969b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1605582964933%26issue%3D20201117&h=07bd5a58\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1605582964933&amp;issue=20201117</a><br />\n<br />\n路透報道，加拿大法院獲悉，華為孟晚舟在加拿大被捕的關鍵證人拒絕出庭作證。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大法院週一恢復審理孟晚舟引渡案，其代表律師Richard Peck於法庭表示，關鍵證人加拿大皇家騎警警官Ben Chang在尋求律師建議後拒絕出庭作證，「令人擔憂」。<br />\n<br />\n根據法庭文件，現已退休的Chang涉嫌將孟晚舟電子設備的詳細情況發送給FBI。 Chang在提交給法庭的書面證詞中否認了這一指控。 Richard Peck在法庭上表示，Chang拒絕作證「將讓人有點擔心」，並稱「他拒絕作證可能會造成一些後果」。"},{"pid":"1976ac04ebc20e4c0cf53ef3ef66b216b25ad4b7","tid":2289696,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"即係點"},{"pid":"615b45799d9e69eaa3cf816d895a42627724ca2e","tid":2289696,"uid":275572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:27:47.000Z","msg":"收左錢？"},{"pid":"2cca66c80b26c0c793c3dcc676d611457c61c271","tid":2289696,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:32:48.000Z","msg":"點樣"},{"pid":"34fa1f0375bbce2f25567f6583e44a544c55c376","tid":2289696,"uid":89641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"捉住左佢屋企人要脅唔好上庭啦，應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930ffb58aa8a943fdb7